properties.property:
The experiment has gone wrong.
Its nature was not technical, but spiritual. A contagious memetic virus escaped and wreaked havoc.
Many people were infected. They soon founded a dangerous sect, and a hostile-to-life doctrine started to gain traction.
To protect civilization from changing forever for the worse, you must perform a therapeutic intervention.
A plasma gun will be your tool.
There are only two rules:
Don't fear the reaper.
Shoot all the messengers of bad news.
Your first target will be an outpost at the galaxy's edge. The sect is trying to gain influence here, hidden from the sight of official institutions.

property.name: message
property.value: At the screen's upper-right corner there's a counter showing how many cultists remain. When you get rid of them all, you will win this mission. Good luck.
